item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

case 6163: c.getThieving().stealFromStall(1892, 20, 1); break;

1892 is the item id, 20 is the exp, and 1 is how many of that item you receive.

such as

case 6163: c.getThieving().stealFromStall(995, 200, 1000000); break;
